[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":476},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fvscode\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F27\u002Fvscode-terminal-integrated-shell-osx-deprecated\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fvscode\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F27\u002Fvscode-terminal-integrated-shell-osx-deprecated\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fvscode\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F27\u002Fvscode-terminal-integrated-shell-osx-deprecated\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fvscode\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F27\u002Fvscode-terminal-integrated-shell-osx-deprecated\u002F":453,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fvscode\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F27\u002Fvscode-terminal-integrated-shell-osx-deprecated\u002F":462},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20210927\u002F2674618084\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":437,"date":438,"description":439,"extension":440,"lang":441,"meta":442,"navigation":397,"path":443,"readingMinutes":444,"seo":445,"standalone":446,"stem":447,"tags":448,"tldr":450,"updated":438,"url":451,"__hash__":452},"content\u002Fen\u002FVSCode\u002Fvscode-terminal-integrated-shell-osx-deprecated.md","`terminal.integrated.shell.osx` Is Deprecated in VSCode — Here's the New Way","8830301173",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":431},"minimark",[11,16,25,29,36,40,43,57,64,74,81,152,159,162,168,171,177,182,265,271,274,338,341,410,414,427],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"intro","Intro",[17,18,19,20,24],"p",{},"Noticed that VSCode's ",[21,22,23],"code",{},"terminal.integrated.shell.osx"," setting stopped working. Here's the cause and the fix.",[12,26,28],{"id":27},"what-happened","What happened",[17,30,31,32,35],{},"VSCode ships updates fast, and we all tend to have our personal dev environment settings. One of mine — ",[21,33,34],{},"\"terminal.integrated.shell.osx\": \"\u002Fbin\u002Fzsh\""," — got flagged for an update, so let me walk through how to migrate it.",[12,37,39],{"id":38},"the-fix","The fix",[17,41,42],{},"VSCode tells you exactly what to do:",[44,45,46],"blockquote",{},[17,47,48,49,52,53,56],{},"This is deprecated. The new recommended way is to create a terminal profile in ",[21,50,51],{},"#terminal.integrated.profiles.osx#"," and set its name as the default value in ",[21,54,55],{},"#terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.osx#",". This will take precedence over the new profile settings, but will change in the future. (2)",[17,58,59],{},[60,61],"img",{"alt":62,"src":63},"Deprecated warning","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fl8IapHP.png",[17,65,66,67,69,70,73],{},"So replace ",[21,68,34],{}," with ",[21,71,72],{},"\"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.osx\": \"zsh\""," and you're set.",[17,75,76,77,80],{},"The other property is ",[21,78,79],{},"terminal.integrated.profiles.osx",", which I think is pretty fun — you can give each terminal profile its own icon. For example, a star:",[82,83,88],"pre",{"className":84,"code":85,"language":86,"meta":87,"style":87},"language-json shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","\"terminal.integrated.profiles.osx\": {\n  \"bash\": {\n      \"path\": \"\u002Fbin\u002Fzsh\",\n      \"icon\": \"star\",\n  }\n},\n","json","",[21,89,90,103,112,127,140,146],{"__ignoreMap":87},[91,92,95,99],"span",{"class":93,"line":94},"line",1,[91,96,98],{"class":97},"sTRMh","\"terminal.integrated.profiles.osx\"",[91,100,102],{"class":101},"sMAXC",": {\n",[91,104,106,110],{"class":93,"line":105},2,[91,107,109],{"class":108},"sKpQp","  \"bash\"",[91,111,102],{"class":101},[91,113,115,118,121,124],{"class":93,"line":114},3,[91,116,117],{"class":108},"      \"path\"",[91,119,120],{"class":101},": ",[91,122,123],{"class":97},"\"\u002Fbin\u002Fzsh\"",[91,125,126],{"class":101},",\n",[91,128,130,133,135,138],{"class":93,"line":129},4,[91,131,132],{"class":108},"      \"icon\"",[91,134,120],{"class":101},[91,136,137],{"class":97},"\"star\"",[91,139,126],{"class":101},[91,141,143],{"class":93,"line":142},5,[91,144,145],{"class":101},"  }\n",[91,147,149],{"class":93,"line":148},6,[91,150,151],{"class":101},"},\n",[17,153,154,155],{},"Original icon:\n",[60,156],{"alt":157,"src":158},"Original icon","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F1AEERaJ.png",[17,160,161],{},"After the tweak:",[17,163,164],{},[60,165],{"alt":166,"src":167},"Star icon","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FcR1fxrY.png",[17,169,170],{},"You can pick from a list of icon names in the dropdown — there are a lot, so I won't list them all:",[17,172,173],{},[60,174],{"alt":175,"src":176},"Icon options","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fcd1nXi0.png",[17,178,179,181],{},[21,180,79],{}," is also nice because you can configure multiple terminal entries with their own styles:",[82,183,185],{"className":84,"code":184,"language":86,"meta":87,"style":87},"\"terminal.integrated.profiles.osx\": {\n  \"bash2\": {\n      \"path\": \"\u002Fbin\u002Fbash\",\n      \"icon\": \"star\",\n  },\n  \"zsh\": {\n      \"path\": \"\u002Fbin\u002Fzsh\",\n      \"icon\": \"star\",\n  }\n},\n",[21,186,187,193,200,211,221,226,233,244,255,260],{"__ignoreMap":87},[91,188,189,191],{"class":93,"line":94},[91,190,98],{"class":97},[91,192,102],{"class":101},[91,194,195,198],{"class":93,"line":105},[91,196,197],{"class":108},"  \"bash2\"",[91,199,102],{"class":101},[91,201,202,204,206,209],{"class":93,"line":114},[91,203,117],{"class":108},[91,205,120],{"class":101},[91,207,208],{"class":97},"\"\u002Fbin\u002Fbash\"",[91,210,126],{"class":101},[91,212,213,215,217,219],{"class":93,"line":129},[91,214,132],{"class":108},[91,216,120],{"class":101},[91,218,137],{"class":97},[91,220,126],{"class":101},[91,222,223],{"class":93,"line":142},[91,224,225],{"class":101},"  },\n",[91,227,228,231],{"class":93,"line":148},[91,229,230],{"class":108},"  \"zsh\"",[91,232,102],{"class":101},[91,234,236,238,240,242],{"class":93,"line":235},7,[91,237,117],{"class":108},[91,239,120],{"class":101},[91,241,123],{"class":97},[91,243,126],{"class":101},[91,245,247,249,251,253],{"class":93,"line":246},8,[91,248,132],{"class":108},[91,250,120],{"class":101},[91,252,137],{"class":97},[91,254,126],{"class":101},[91,256,258],{"class":93,"line":257},9,[91,259,145],{"class":101},[91,261,263],{"class":93,"line":262},10,[91,264,151],{"class":101},[17,266,267],{},[60,268],{"alt":269,"src":270},"Multiple profiles","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FV7B4vvN.png",[17,272,273],{},"Heads up: the above is for macOS. For Windows it's:",[82,275,277],{"className":84,"code":276,"language":86,"meta":87,"style":87},"\"terminal.integrated.profiles.windows\": {\n    \"PowerShell -NoProfile\": {\n      \"source\": \"PowerShell\",\n      \"args\": [\"-NoProfile\"]\n    }\n},\n\"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.windows\": \"my-pwsh\"\n",[21,278,279,286,293,305,319,324,328],{"__ignoreMap":87},[91,280,281,284],{"class":93,"line":94},[91,282,283],{"class":97},"\"terminal.integrated.profiles.windows\"",[91,285,102],{"class":101},[91,287,288,291],{"class":93,"line":105},[91,289,290],{"class":108},"    \"PowerShell -NoProfile\"",[91,292,102],{"class":101},[91,294,295,298,300,303],{"class":93,"line":114},[91,296,297],{"class":108},"      \"source\"",[91,299,120],{"class":101},[91,301,302],{"class":97},"\"PowerShell\"",[91,304,126],{"class":101},[91,306,307,310,313,316],{"class":93,"line":129},[91,308,309],{"class":108},"      \"args\"",[91,311,312],{"class":101},": [",[91,314,315],{"class":97},"\"-NoProfile\"",[91,317,318],{"class":101},"]\n",[91,320,321],{"class":93,"line":142},[91,322,323],{"class":101},"    }\n",[91,325,326],{"class":93,"line":148},[91,327,151],{"class":101},[91,329,330,333,335],{"class":93,"line":235},[91,331,332],{"class":97},"\"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.windows\"",[91,334,120],{"class":101},[91,336,337],{"class":97},"\"my-pwsh\"\n",[17,339,340],{},"For Linux:",[82,342,344],{"className":84,"code":343,"language":86,"meta":87,"style":87},"\"terminal.integrated.profiles.linux\": {\n  \"zsh (login)\": {\n    \"path\": \"zsh\",\n    \"args\": [\"-l\"]\n  }\n}\n\n\"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.linux\": \"zsh\",\n",[21,345,346,353,360,372,384,388,393,399],{"__ignoreMap":87},[91,347,348,351],{